doeshunchentootwork - Test Hunchentoot on your system

HOMEPAGE

http://doeshunchentootwork.yellosoft.us/

INSTALL

1. Edit doeshunchentootwork.lisp.
2. Modify the shebang to point to your Common Lisp implementation.
3. Run chmod a+x doeshunchentootwork.lisp
4. Edit hunchentoot.sh.
5. Modify $HUNCHENTOOT_DIR to point to this directory.
6. Modify stop and restart cases to kill your Common Lisp implementation.
7. Follow daemon installation instructions.
8. Run service hunchentoot start
